28
00:04:39.112 --> 00:04:40.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>分かりました</c.japanese>

29
00:04:41.155 --> 00:04:46.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>でも 悪いやつを止めるのは
