30
00:04:46.953 --> 00:04:47.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ライト</c.japanese>

31
00:04:48.788 --> 00:04:53.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あんな形で母親を
