33
00:04:58.756 --> 00:05:00.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>だが私は違う</c.japanese>

34
00:05:01.134 --> 00:05:03.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
