41
00:07:00.586 --> 00:07:01.504 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰だ？</c.japanese>

42
00:07:53.556 --> 00:07:54.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>助けて！</c.japanese>

43
00:07:55.057 --> 00:07:55.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰か！</c.japanese>

44
00:08:07.069 --> 00:08:08.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何なんだ？</c.japanese>

45
00:08:29.425 --> 00:08:31.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>始めようか</c.japanese>

46
