48
00:08:47.610 --> 00:08:51.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>巨大な悪魔が出てくる夢を</c.japanese>

49
00:08:51.572 --> 00:08:55.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そのとおり
夢ってのはいい考えだ</c.japanese>

50
00:08:55.952 --> 00:09:00.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>夢の中では楽しい思いが
出来るもんな</c.japanese>

51
00:09:00.748 --> 00:09:05.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>夢を見てるのなら
楽しめばいい</c.japanese>

52
00:09:07.755 --> 00:09:08.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>聞け</c.japanese>

53
00:09:12.468 --> 00:09:13.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>見てみろよ</c.japanese>

54
00:09:22.645 --> 00:09:23.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ほらよ</c.japanese>

55
00:09:24.105 --> 00:09:26.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ケニー　やめてよ</c.japanese>

56
00:09:26.524 --> 00:09:28.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>放してったら</c.japanese>

57
00:09:30.778 --> 00:09:32.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ダサいやつだな</c.japanese>

58
00:09:32.697 --> 00:09:36.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お前は夢の中で
