59
00:09:36.534 --> 00:09:40.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>うまく片付けることが出来る</c.japanese>

60
00:09:40.871 --> 00:09:46.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ケニーの名前を書いて
