63
00:10:02.226 --> 00:10:03.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>さあ 書けよ</c.japanese>

64
00:10:04.353 --> 00:10:05.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>助けてやれ</c.japanese>

65
