<c.japanese>〝ケニー･ドイル〞</c.japanese>

68
00:10:28.294 --> 00:10:32.089 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:74.81%,start 
<c.japanese>〝ケニー･ドイル〞</c.japanese>

69
00:10:28.294 --> 00:10:32.089 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>その調子だ
