79
00:10:58.115 --> 00:10:59.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>返してよ</c.japanese>

80
00:11:00.117 --> 00:11:01.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
