85
00:11:49.041 --> 00:11:51.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>さっき その目で見ただろう？</c.japanese>

86
00:11:51.669 --> 00:11:55.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>このノートで何が出来るか
