87
00:12:36.630 --> 00:12:37.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>友だちか？</c.japanese>

88
00:12:38.424 --> 00:12:39.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰が？</c.japanese>

89
00:12:39.675 --> 00:12:41.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>死んだ生徒だ</c.japanese>

90
00:12:42.636 --> 00:12:44.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いや　嫌われ者だった</c.japanese>

91
00:12:46.307 --> 00:12:47.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>話をするか？</c.japanese>

92
00:12:50.186 --> 00:12:50.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いや</c.japanese>

93
00:12:50.811 --> 00:12:53.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>なぜ まだ学校にいた？</c.japanese>

94
00:12:53.272 --> 00:12:57.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>宿題の代行がバレて
