95
00:12:57.401 --> 00:13:00.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お前は平気で不正をするのか</c.japanese>

96
00:13:01.405 --> 00:13:02.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>違う</c.japanese>

97
00:13:03.657 --> 00:13:06.494 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いじめを止めようとして…</c.japanese>

98
00:13:09.455 --> 00:13:12.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>父さんには分からないよ</c.japanese>

99
00:13:12.208 --> 00:13:14.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>優秀なお前と違うから？</c.japanese>

100
00:13:14.418 --> 00:13:18.380 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>父さんはいつも
本当の問題を放置して―</c.japanese>

101
00:13:18.506 --> 00:13:23.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>つまらないことにばかり
目を光らせる</c.japanese>

102
00:13:23.177 --> 00:13:25.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>警察が正しく行動しないと</c.japanese>

103
00:13:26.347 --> 00:13:28.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>市民は信頼しない</c.japanese>

104
00:13:32.311 --> 00:13:34.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>本気でやってほしいよ</c.japanese>

105
00:13:34.939 --> 00:13:35.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>警官だろ？</c.japanese>

106
00:13:36.065 --> 00:13:39.693 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>妻を殺した男が無罪でも
