107
00:13:39.818 --> 00:13:41.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>平気だと思うか？</c.japanese>

108
00:13:41.445 --> 00:13:46.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>母さんをひき殺し
恋人を半殺しにしたのに―</c.japanese>

109
00:13:46.659 --> 00:13:49.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>スコマルは金で保釈された</c.japanese>

110
00:13:49.662 --> 00:13:52.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>父さんはいつも何もしない</c.japanese>

111
00:13:53.082 --> 00:13:57.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お前がそんなことを
