112
00:13:57.294 --> 00:13:59.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>事故で動揺してるからだ</c.japanese>

113
00:13:59.755 --> 00:14:01.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>黙ったほうがいいぞ</c.japanese>

114
00:14:28.325 --> 00:14:32.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ルール64　切り取った
ページも同じ効力を持つ”</c.japanese>

115
00:14:34.582 --> 00:14:38.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ルール95　所有者以外でも
名前は書き込める”</c.japanese>

116
00:14:38.878 --> 00:14:41.005 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ルールが多いな</c.japanese>

117
00:14:43.757 --> 00:14:45.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“<c.ruby_before><ruby>ラ<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before><c.ruby_before><ruby>ユ<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before><c.ruby_before><ruby>ク<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before>を信じるな”</c.japanese>

118
00:14:45.843 --> 00:14:48.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“彼はペットでも
友でもない”</c.japanese>

119
00:15:47.529 --> 00:15:48.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>おい</c.japanese>

120
00:15:49.156 --> 00:15:50.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>読み方は<c.ruby_before><ruby>リ<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before><c.ruby_before><ruby>ュ<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before><c.ruby_before><ruby>ー<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before><c.ruby_before><ruby>ク<rt>•</rt></ruby></c.ruby_before>だ</c.japanese>

121
00:15:52.868 --> 00:15:53.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>リューク</c.japanese>

122
00:15:55.371 --> 00:15:56.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そうか</c.japanese>

123
00:15:56.789 --> 00:15:58.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>間違えて悪かった</c.japanese>

124
00:15:59.625 --> 00:16:02.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>デスノートで何をすれば？</c.japanese>

125
00:16:02.211 --> 00:16:03.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何がしたい？</c.japanese>

126
00:16:04.046 --> 00:16:10.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰がどんな風に死ぬか
僕が決められるんだよね</c.japanese>

127
00:16:10.511 --> 00:16:14.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰でも死ぬ時は
死神の世話になる</c.japanese>

128
00:16:14.682 --> 00:16:18.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>我々は死の状況を操れるんだ</c.japanese>

129
00:16:18.519 --> 00:16:20.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>もちろん制限はある</c.japanese>

130
00:16:21.397 --> 00:16:27.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ルール20　行動を操れるのは
死ぬ前２日間のみ”</c.japanese>

131
00:16:28.529 --> 00:16:30.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>２日間… 長い指だね</c.japanese>

132
00:16:30.197 --> 00:16:33.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ルール28　物理的に可能な
