133
00:16:33.951 --> 00:16:36.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“トイレでサメに
襲われる”はダメだ</c.japanese>

134
00:16:37.663 --> 00:16:39.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>面白そうだがな</c.japanese>

135
00:16:40.165 --> 00:16:41.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ノートはどこから？</c.japanese>

136
00:16:42.334 --> 00:16:45.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>大昔から受け継がれてる</c.japanese>

137
00:16:45.170 --> 00:16:47.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>君が僕に渡そうと？</c.japanese>

138
00:16:47.589 --> 00:16:52.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>前の所有者が死んで
新たな所有者を探してる</c.japanese>

139
00:16:53.220 --> 00:16:54.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>不要なら？</c.japanese>

140
00:16:54.263 --> 00:16:57.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>要らないなら俺に返せ</c.japanese>

141
00:16:58.225 --> 00:16:58.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>出来るの？</c.japanese>

142
00:16:59.101 --> 00:17:05.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>７日間 放置すればいい
俺は新たな所有者を探す</c.japanese>

143
00:17:05.607 --> 00:17:07.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>余白に“君を信じるな”と…</c.japanese>

144
00:17:08.527 --> 00:17:12.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ルールや警告は
もういいだろう？</c.japanese>

145
00:17:29.673 --> 00:17:32.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“今回の被害者は警官の妻”</c.japanese>

146
00:17:37.306 --> 00:17:40.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“スコマルに無罪評決
陪審員を買収”</c.japanese>

147
00:17:43.979 --> 00:17:48.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>名前と顔が分かってれば
それで十分だ</c.japanese>

148
00:17:58.577 --> 00:18:00.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“アントニー･スコマル”</c.japanese>

149
00:18:53.674 --> 00:18:54.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ターナーだ</c.japanese>

150
00:18:55.259 --> 00:18:56.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いや 大丈夫だ</c.japanese>

151
00:18:58.428 --> 00:18:59.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何だって？</c.japanese>

152
00:19:00.430 --> 00:19:01.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>本当か？</c.japanese>

153
00:19:06.770 --> 00:19:07.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>分かった</c.japanese>

154
00:19:07.813 --> 00:19:09.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>後でな</c.japanese>

155
00:19:09.731 --> 00:19:10.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>じゃ</c.japanese>

156
00:19:12.651 --> 00:19:13.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いいか</c.japanese>

157
00:19:14.236 --> 00:19:16.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ちょっと待って</c.japanese>

158
00:19:16.488 --> 00:19:17.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いいよ</c.japanese>

159
00:19:21.076 --> 00:19:22.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何してた？</c.japanese>

160
00:19:23.036 --> 00:19:25.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>机でうたた寝してた</c.japanese>

161
