<c.japanese>食事中 喉にナイフが刺さった</c.japanese>

164
00:19:34.464 --> 00:19:35.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ひどいな</c.japanese>

165
00:19:36.800 --> 00:19:37.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>うれしい？</c.japanese>

166
