<c.japanese>ああ　不謹慎だがな</c.japanese>

167
00:19:43.265 --> 00:19:44.266 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>母さんは―</c.japanese>

168
00:19:46.393 --> 00:19:51.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>型破りで 俺と意見が
