170
00:19:59.698 --> 00:20:02.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あんなこと言って ごめん</c.japanese>

171
00:20:05.495 --> 00:20:06.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>愛してる</c.japanese>

172
00:20:07.789 --> 00:20:08.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕もだ</c.japanese>

173
00:20:49.748 --> 00:20:50.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>悲しんでる？</c.japanese>

174
00:20:52.125 --> 00:20:53.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何のこと？</c.japanese>

175
00:20:54.753 --> 00:20:55.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ケニーよ</c.japanese>

176
00:20:56.505 --> 00:20:58.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>気の毒だよね</c.japanese>

177
00:21:02.469 --> 00:21:03.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ウソだわ</c.japanese>

178
00:21:04.096 --> 00:21:07.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あんなやつ
