179
00:21:08.016 --> 00:21:09.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>見てみたかった</c.japanese>

180
00:21:10.310 --> 00:21:12.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>頭が転がったって</c.japanese>

181
00:21:12.604 --> 00:21:14.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>首から上が吹っ飛んでた</c.japanese>

182
00:21:14.898 --> 00:21:15.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>まさにね</c.japanese>

183
00:21:16.066 --> 00:21:16.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>見たの？</c.japanese>

184
00:21:25.784 --> 00:21:26.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私はミア</c.japanese>

185
00:21:26.785 --> 00:21:30.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>よろしく　君の名前は知ってる</c.japanese>

186
00:21:31.123 --> 00:21:33.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ライト･ターナーよね？</c.japanese>

187
00:21:34.835 --> 00:21:37.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>なぜ 僕の名前を？</c.japanese>

188
00:21:37.296 --> 00:21:39.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>見たことを詳しく教えて</c.japanese>

189
00:21:39.631 --> 00:21:41.425 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>居残りは君のせいだ</c.japanese>

190
00:21:42.384 --> 00:21:43.427 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ごめん</c.japanese>

191
00:21:44.386 --> 00:21:47.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>治療のために先生を呼んだの</c.japanese>

192
00:21:47.431 --> 00:21:52.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>他人の宿題が鞄に
