193
00:21:53.812 --> 00:21:54.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それも宿題？</c.japanese>

194
00:21:54.980 --> 00:21:56.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>これ？　違うよ</c.japanese>

195
00:21:57.065 --> 00:21:59.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“デスノート”って？</c.japanese>

196
00:21:59.318 --> 00:22:00.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>これは…</c.japanese>

197
00:22:00.569 --> 00:22:01.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなたの？</c.japanese>

198
00:22:03.822 --> 00:22:05.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>教えない</c.japanese>

199
00:22:07.326 --> 00:22:08.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そう</c.japanese>

200
00:22:08.243 --> 00:22:09.328 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>知りたい？</c.japanese>

201
00:22:11.955 --> 00:22:12.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ええ</c.japanese>

202
00:22:12.622 --> 00:22:14.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>教えるよ</c.japanese>

203
00:22:15.834 --> 00:22:16.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>来て</c.japanese>

204
00:22:28.346 --> 00:22:30.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>まさか詩集なの？</c.japanese>

205
00:22:30.348 --> 00:22:34.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>彼が見えても
怖がらないように</c.japanese>

206
00:22:35.395 --> 00:22:37.397 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰が見えるの？</c.japanese>

207
00:22:37.647 --> 00:22:38.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>後ろに</c.japanese>

208
00:22:42.736 --> 00:22:43.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>平気だ</c.japanese>

209
00:22:44.905 --> 00:22:45.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何のこと？</c.japanese>

210
00:22:46.114 --> 00:22:48.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>所有者にしか見えない</c.japanese>

211
00:22:49.117 --> 00:22:52.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“このノートに名前を
書かれた人間は死ぬ”</c.japanese>

212
00:22:53.830 --> 00:22:54.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ヘタな詩</c.japanese>

213
00:22:54.748 --> 00:22:57.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>違うよ
