214
00:23:00.962 --> 00:23:02.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ケニー･ドイル　頭部切断”</c.japanese>

215
00:23:04.966 --> 00:23:07.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕がやったんだ</c.japanese>

216
00:23:08.011 --> 00:23:10.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕には死神がついてる</c.japanese>

217
00:23:17.062 --> 00:23:18.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>もう行くわ</c.japanese>

218
00:23:18.522 --> 00:23:22.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>待って　いいものを見せるから</c.japanese>

219
00:23:23.318 --> 00:23:24.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“犯罪　中継”</c.japanese>

220
