<c.japanese>〝シアトルで人質事件</c.japanese>
<c.japanese>生中継〞</c.japanese>

222
00:23:27.614 --> 00:23:28.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>これだ</c.japanese>

223
00:23:28.907 --> 00:23:28.907 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:71.69%,start 
<c.japanese>〝シアトルで人質事件</c.japanese>
<c.japanese>生中継〞</c.japanese>

224
