00:36:47.455 --> 00:36:49.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私と寝る男も殺す？</c.japanese>

447
00:36:50.124 --> 00:36:52.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それは… 殺すよ</c.japanese>

448
00:36:53.502 --> 00:36:54.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺すのね</c.japanese>

449
00:36:55.087 --> 00:36:58.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>でもネット上の噂だけじゃ
殺せないよ</c.japanese>

450
00:37:01.052 --> 00:37:02.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>噂じゃないわ</c.japanese>

451
00:37:02.762 --> 00:37:05.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>苦しんでる人は実際にいる</c.japanese>

452
00:37:07.642 --> 00:37:08.684 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>救ってあげて</c.japanese>

453
00:37:52.561 --> 00:37:53.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>随分若いな</c.japanese>

454
00:37:55.022 --> 00:37:57.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>顔は見せないのか？</c.japanese>

455
00:37:58.359 --> 00:38:02.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>最近は人を
信頼する気になれません</c.japanese>

456
00:38:02.571 --> 00:38:05.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>証拠品も安全な場所に
移しました</c.japanese>

457
00:38:05.908 --> 00:38:09.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>確かに断りもなく
移したようだな</c.japanese>

458
00:38:10.246 --> 00:38:13.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>優秀な捜査チームですね</c.japanese>

459
00:38:14.041 --> 00:38:16.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>チームは ないも同然だ</c.japanese>

460
00:38:17.211 --> 00:38:18.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなた一人で？</c.japanese>

461
00:38:20.589 --> 00:38:22.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>大した捜査力だ</c.japanese>

462
00:38:22.925 --> 00:38:25.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>では 座ってください</c.japanese>

463
00:38:31.767 --> 00:38:32.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お教えします</c.japanese>

464
00:38:33.477 --> 00:38:36.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラが殺した１人目は
この男</c.japanese>

465
00:38:36.480 --> 00:38:42.695 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>４月15日　元妻子を人質にした
ジェームズ･ブローディです</c.japanese>

466
00:38:42.987 --> 00:38:45.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あの事件は覚えてる</c.japanese>

467
00:38:45.281 --> 00:38:50.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>犯人の奇妙な行動は
麻薬が原因と思われましたが</c.japanese>

468
00:38:50.703 --> 00:38:53.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>薬物検査は陰性でした</c.japanese>

469
00:38:53.456 --> 00:38:58.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>立てこもりが中継されたのは
シアトルだけです</c.japanese>

470
00:38:58.336 --> 00:38:59.420 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラはこの街に</c.japanese>

471
00:38:59.587 --> 00:39:02.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>警察のデータにアクセスし</c.japanese>

472
00:39:02.173 --> 00:39:05.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>市外に情報が漏れてないと
確認しました</c.japanese>

473
00:39:05.885 --> 00:39:06.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>市外に情報が漏れてないと
確認しました</c.japanese>

474
00:39:05.885 --> 00:39:06.218 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:71.69%,start 
<c.japanese>〝事件報告書〞</c.japanese>

475
00:39:06.218 --> 00:39:06.510 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:71.69%,start 
<c.japanese>〝事件報告書〞</c.japanese>

476
00:39:06.510 --> 00:39:07.053 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:71.69%,start 
<c.japanese>〝事件報告書〞</c.japanese>

477
00:39:06.510 --> 00:39:07.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>警察サイトに侵入したのか？</c.japanese>

478
00:39:07.053 --> 00:39:09.096 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>警察サイトに侵入したのか？</c.japanese>

479
00:39:09.430 --> 00:39:13.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラも内部から
アクセスしています</c.japanese>

480
00:39:14.602 --> 00:39:15.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラは警官？</c.japanese>

481
00:39:16.354 --> 00:39:21.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>アクセス可能な警官と
事件発生日の照合リストです</c.japanese>

482
00:39:21.942 --> 00:39:27.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰がいつ どこにいたか
調べてください</c.japanese>

483
00:39:27.323 --> 00:39:28.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>君は何を？</c.japanese>

484
00:39:28.407 --> 00:39:30.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラに語りかけます</c.japanese>

485
00:39:30.993 --> 00:39:32.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そりゃいい</c.japanese>

486
00:39:56.936 --> 00:39:58.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ニュースを見て</c.japanese>

487
00:40:01.232 --> 00:40:06.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラと呼ばれる人物は既に
400人以上を殺しています</c.japanese>

488
00:40:06.695 --> 00:40:07.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何だと</c.japanese>

489
00:40:07.780 --> 00:40:11.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺す人物をどう選ぶかは
分かりました</c.japanese>

490
00:40:12.243 --> 00:40:16.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>全員が名前と顔を
報道されていました</c.japanese>

491
00:40:17.581 --> 00:40:20.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラは万能の神
などではなく―</c.japanese>

492
00:40:21.502 --> 00:40:24.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>我々と同じ
人間にすぎません</c.japanese>

493
00:40:25.464 --> 00:40:26.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そして臆病です</c.japanese>

494
00:40:27.716 --> 00:40:31.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>不相応な力を振るう
幼稚な人物で―</c.japanese>

495
00:40:31.804 --> 00:40:34.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>自分は捕まらないと
勘違いしている</c.japanese>

496
00:40:35.057 --> 00:40:39.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラ　見ているか？
私はお前を追い詰める</c.japanese>

497
00:40:40.729 --> 00:40:44.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>イヤなら
今すぐ私を殺してみろ</c.japanese>

498
00:40:52.158 --> 00:40:53.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>応援したいね</c.japanese>

499
00:40:53.742 --> 00:40:54.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>黙ってろ</c.japanese>

500
00:40:56.120 --> 00:40:57.204 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺せない？</c.japanese>

501
00:40:58.456 --> 00:41:01.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それではキラ</c.japanese>

502
00:41:01.333 --> 00:41:04.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>近いうちに直接会おう</c.japanese>

503
00:41:04.837 --> 00:41:06.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰なの？</c.japanese>

504
00:41:12.094 --> 00:41:13.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何のつもりだ</c.japanese>

505
00:41:15.764 --> 00:41:19.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラが誰かを殺すには
条件があります</c.japanese>

506
00:41:20.060 --> 00:41:22.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>名前と顔を知ること</c.japanese>

507
00:41:22.688 --> 00:41:25.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>過去の例から明らかです</c.japanese>

508
00:41:25.191 --> 00:41:26.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>挑発したのか？</c.japanese>

509
00:41:27.151 --> 00:41:29.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>名前と顔を伏せたから―</c.japanese>

510
00:41:29.612 --> 00:41:33.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラは私を
殺したくても殺せない</c.japanese>

511
00:41:33.699 --> 00:41:34.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>間違いなら？</c.japanese>

512
00:41:36.327 --> 00:41:38.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私は死にますが―</c.japanese>

513
00:41:39.205 --> 00:41:41.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ヒントは得られる</c.japanese>

514
00:41:43.209 --> 00:41:44.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いつも こうなのか？</c.japanese>

515
00:42:08.692 --> 00:42:10.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜査は進んでる？</c.japanese>

516
00:42:12.196 --> 00:42:15.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>進展はあったが先は長い</c.japanese>

517
00:42:16.492 --> 00:42:18.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>記者会見を見たよ</c.japanese>

518
00:42:19.954 --> 00:42:22.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>顔を隠してたの誰？</c.japanese>

519
00:42:22.248 --> 00:42:25.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あの格好は好きか？　俺もだ</c.japanese>

520
00:42:28.462 --> 00:42:31.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>彼はＬと呼ばれる探偵だ</c.japanese>

521
00:42:31.757 --> 00:42:33.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>本名は知らないの？</c.japanese>

522
00:42:33.884 --> 00:42:38.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ワタリという代理人が
いること以外は謎だよ</c.japanese>

523
00:42:39.181 --> 00:42:41.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>Ｌはすごく優秀だ</c.japanese>

524
00:42:41.350 --> 00:42:43.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>だったらＬがキラかも</c.japanese>

525
00:42:45.521 --> 00:42:48.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>違うな　彼は長年
警察に協力してきた</c.japanese>

526
00:42:49.316 --> 00:42:53.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺だって目の前に
キラがいたら気付くさ</c.japanese>

527
00:42:53.237 --> 00:42:54.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そうだね</c.japanese>

528
00:42:54.989 --> 00:42:56.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捕まったらどうなる？</c.japanese>

529
00:42:58.033 --> 00:43:00.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>400人以上も殺したんだ</c.japanese>

530
00:43:01.412 --> 00:43:06.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>死刑にするか
研究のため精神分析するかで</c.japanese>

531
00:43:06.584 --> 00:43:08.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>意見が割れるだろう</c.japanese>

532
00:43:10.504 --> 00:43:11.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>平気か？</c.japanese>

533
00:43:12.298 --> 00:43:13.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ああ</c.japanese>

534
00:43:30.941 --> 00:43:32.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>息子を尾行だと？</c.japanese>

535
00:43:32.693 --> 00:43:38.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなたも捜査されるべき
人物に含まれます</c.japanese>

536
00:43:38.198 --> 00:43:42.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺の話じゃない
息子を尾行してる件だ</c.japanese>

537
00:43:42.703 --> 00:43:46.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなたはキラではないと
確認しましたが―</c.japanese>

538
00:43:46.915 --> 00:43:50.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>息子さんは
まだ捜査の対象です</c.japanese>

539
00:43:51.003 --> 00:43:54.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>データにアクセス
可能ですからね</c.japanese>

540
00:43:54.840 --> 00:43:56.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>まだ子どもだ</c.japanese>

541
00:43:56.300 --> 00:43:57.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ですが―</c.japanese>

542
00:43:58.552 --> 00:44:00.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>極めて賢い</c.japanese>

543
00:44:00.304 --> 00:44:03.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>息子に関することなら
俺に聞け</c.japanese>

544
00:44:11.273 --> 00:44:16.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕を疑っても証拠はない
何もしなければ諦めるさ</c.japanese>

545
00:44:16.945 --> 00:44:18.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“何もしない”？</c.japanese>

546
00:44:18.906 --> 00:44:20.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ノートを使わない</c.japanese>

547
00:44:20.658 --> 00:44:21.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それは本心？</c.japanese>

548
00:44:22.117 --> 00:44:25.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>尾行者を殺せよ　顔と名前で</c.japanese>

549
00:44:25.245 --> 00:44:25.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>イヤだ</c.japanese>

550
00:44:26.038 --> 00:44:26.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何が？</c.japanese>

551
00:44:27.373 --> 00:44:28.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>リュークに言った</c.japanese>

552
00:44:28.582 --> 00:44:31.669 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺は彼女の考えが
いいと思うぞ</c.japanese>

553
00:44:31.794 --> 00:44:32.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何て？</c.japanese>

554
00:44:33.045 --> 00:44:34.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>リュークが？　別に</c.japanese>

555
00:44:36.131 --> 00:44:37.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私たちが正義よ</c.japanese>

556
00:44:37.716 --> 00:44:43.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕を尾行中のＦＢＩ捜査官が
死ねば 僕が疑われる</c.japanese>

557
00:44:43.847 --> 00:44:47.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>尾行中の捜査官
全員を殺せば―</c.japanese>

558
00:44:47.267 --> 00:44:51.063 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなただけに疑いが
かかることはない</c.japanese>

559
00:44:51.188 --> 00:44:52.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ひどすぎる</c.japanese>

560
00:44:52.314 --> 00:44:53.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>やるべきよ</c.japanese>

561
00:44:53.399 --> 00:44:55.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>所有者が僕でよかったよ</c.japanese>

562
00:44:58.278 --> 00:45:00.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>最近 キラの動きが
ないのは―</c.japanese>

563
00:45:00.823 --> 00:45:07.037 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>大規模な捜査による効果だと
警察は主張しています</c.japanese>

564
00:45:07.329 --> 00:45:12.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>しかしキラ信者からは
批判の声が上がり始めました</c.japanese>

565
00:45:12.751 --> 00:45:16.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜査により
キラが活動していない現在</c.japanese>

566
00:45:16.839 --> 00:45:19.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>また犯罪が
増えているためです</c.japanese>

567
00:45:19.967 --> 00:45:20.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>帰るの？</c.japanese>

568
00:45:21.468 --> 00:45:23.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>やることがある</c.japanese>

569
00:45:23.971 --> 00:45:29.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ニュースに出てた殺人犯の
名前をメモしておく？</c.japanese>

570
00:45:29.852 --> 00:45:31.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>じゃ 明日</c.japanese>

571
00:45:53.375 --> 00:45:56.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>パール長官　
支局から報告です</c.japanese>

572
00:45:57.463 --> 00:45:59.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>容疑者全員の監視を…</c.japanese>

573
00:46:07.890 --> 00:46:10.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ＦＢＩ長官が急死しました</c.japanese>

574
00:46:10.934 --> 00:46:13.562 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>全捜査官に連絡を</c.japanese>

575
00:46:19.860 --> 00:46:20.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>フランクスです</c.japanese>

576
00:46:21.028 --> 00:46:25.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>直ちに任務を中断し
病院へ行ってください</c.japanese>

577
00:46:26.533 --> 00:46:27.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>フランクス捜査官</c.japanese>

578
00:46:28.410 --> 00:46:30.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>聞こえますか？</c.japanese>

579
00:47:11.245 --> 00:47:14.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ＦＢＩ捜査官12人の自殺は―</c.japanese>

580
00:47:14.498 --> 00:47:17.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラの仕業だと思われます</c.japanese>

581
00:47:17.292 --> 00:47:20.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜査機関への攻撃は
初めてです</c.japanese>

582
00:47:21.046 --> 00:47:22.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ライト　待って</c.japanese>

583
00:47:22.256 --> 00:47:23.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>リュークが殺した</c.japanese>

584
00:47:23.966 --> 00:47:24.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>まさか</c.japanese>

585
00:47:24.716 --> 00:47:27.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ルールに抜け穴があるんだ</c.japanese>

586
00:47:27.344 --> 00:47:29.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>死神を敵に回す気？</c.japanese>

587
00:47:30.138 --> 00:47:34.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>落ち着いて
よく考えたほうがいいわ</c.japanese>

588
00:47:35.978 --> 00:47:36.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>イヤだ</c.japanese>

589
00:47:40.941 --> 00:47:41.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>リューク！</c.japanese>

590
00:47:42.609 --> 00:47:47.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺は犬じゃない
呼べば応えると思うな</c.japanese>

591
00:47:47.823 --> 00:47:49.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜査官を殺した？</c.japanese>

592
00:47:49.908 --> 00:47:50.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>さあな</c.japanese>

593
00:47:51.243 --> 00:47:54.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕が殺す　それがルールだ</c.japanese>

594
00:47:54.288 --> 00:47:55.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ルールは誰が？</c.japanese>

595
00:47:55.747 --> 00:47:56.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>誰の味方だ？</c.japanese>

596
00:47:56.957 --> 00:48:01.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>味方も何も
これはただのゲームだが―</c.japanese>

597
00:48:02.045 --> 00:48:04.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お前の手には負えないな</c.japanese>

598
00:48:04.464 --> 00:48:05.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ノートを手放せ</c.japanese>

599
00:48:05.924 --> 00:48:08.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>彼女ともケンカ続きだろ</c.japanese>

600
00:48:08.719 --> 00:48:11.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺もお前から離れたいしな</c.japanese>

601
00:48:12.097 --> 00:48:14.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ノートは渡さない</c.japanese>

602
00:48:14.433 --> 00:48:16.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お前の名前も書くぞ</c.japanese>

603
00:48:19.896 --> 00:48:21.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>書いてみろよ</c.japanese>

604
00:48:22.482 --> 00:48:25.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>過去に試みた連中が
書けたのは―</c.japanese>

605
00:48:26.028 --> 00:48:28.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>最初の２文字だけだ</c.japanese>

606
00:48:44.963 --> 00:48:47.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>緊急生中継をお届けします</c.japanese>

607
00:48:47.841 --> 00:48:48.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>これは？</c.japanese>

608
00:48:48.842 --> 00:48:51.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ターナー捜査本部長による
会見です</c.japanese>

609
00:48:51.762 --> 00:48:52.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>マズい</c.japanese>

610
00:48:52.721 --> 00:48:56.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラに幻想を抱く人もいます</c.japanese>

611
00:48:56.308 --> 00:49:00.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>しかし実際は
ＦＢＩ捜査官を殺し―</c.japanese>

612
00:49:00.687 --> 00:49:04.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>保身に徹する臆病で
卑劣な犯罪者です</c.japanese>

613
00:49:05.192 --> 00:49:10.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラは尊敬や崇拝に
値するような存在ではないし</c.japanese>

614
00:49:11.114 --> 00:49:14.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>恐れるべき存在でも
ありません</c.japanese>

615
00:49:14.534 --> 00:49:16.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いいか　キラ</c.japanese>

616
00:49:17.704 --> 00:49:19.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺を殺しても</c.japanese>

617
00:49:19.289 --> 00:49:21.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>別の者が立ち上がり…</c.japanese>

618
00:49:21.458 --> 00:49:23.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺される覚悟で？</c.japanese>

619
00:49:23.710 --> 00:49:27.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>どこまでもお前を追い詰める</c.japanese>

620
00:49:27.297 --> 00:49:28.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>恐れてない</c.japanese>

621
00:49:28.465 --> 00:49:29.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>我々は必ず―</c.japanese>

622
00:49:29.716 --> 00:49:31.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お前を捕まえる</c.japanese>

623
00:49:38.850 --> 00:49:39.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>どこ？</c.japanese>

624
00:49:41.061 --> 00:49:42.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>待てよ　父さんだぞ</c.japanese>

625
00:49:42.938 --> 00:49:45.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺せって挑発してた</c.japanese>

626
00:49:46.233 --> 00:49:48.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラを侮辱したわ</c.japanese>

627
00:49:48.402 --> 00:49:49.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>でも殺せない</c.japanese>

628
00:49:49.611 --> 00:49:52.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それにキラは
もう正義じゃない</c.japanese>

629
00:49:54.700 --> 00:49:57.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラの裁きは人を救った</c.japanese>

630
00:49:58.745 --> 00:50:00.038 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>お母さんを忘れた？</c.japanese>

631
00:50:02.999 --> 00:50:05.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>このままじゃ 捕まる</c.japanese>

632
00:50:06.628 --> 00:50:09.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>やめたいなら抜けていい</c.japanese>

633
00:50:14.636 --> 00:50:16.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>やめるのね？</c.japanese>

634
00:50:17.973 --> 00:50:19.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>分からない</c.japanese>

635
00:50:31.028 --> 00:50:32.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>見事でした</c.japanese>

636
00:50:32.404 --> 00:50:35.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>本当に
死ぬ覚悟はありますか？</c.japanese>

637
00:50:35.574 --> 00:50:36.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>必要ならな</c.japanese>

638
00:50:38.702 --> 00:50:41.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラは決断に
時間がかかってます</c.japanese>

639
00:50:51.423 --> 00:50:52.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>どうした</c.japanese>

640
00:51:01.057 --> 00:51:02.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>電話に出ないと</c.japanese>

641
00:51:06.730 --> 00:51:07.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ターナーだ</c.japanese>

642
00:51:07.606 --> 00:51:08.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>Ｌです</c.japanese>

643
00:51:08.732 --> 00:51:10.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>まだ 生きてますね</c.japanese>

644
00:51:11.193 --> 00:51:12.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ああ</c.japanese>

645
00:51:12.319 --> 00:51:14.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>すばらしい</c.japanese>

646
00:51:19.409 --> 00:51:20.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>父さんは立派だ</c.japanese>

647
00:51:27.542 --> 00:51:29.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いいか　キラ</c.japanese>

648
00:51:29.544 --> 00:51:30.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>俺を殺しても…</c.japanese>

649
00:51:31.087 --> 00:51:31.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>失礼します</c.japanese>

650
00:51:32.714 --> 00:51:34.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ライトがキラだ</c.japanese>

651
00:51:35.675 --> 00:51:37.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何時間 起きてますか？</c.japanese>

652
00:51:38.303 --> 00:51:39.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>31時間</c.japanese>

653
00:51:40.013 --> 00:51:42.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>睡眠は良い推理に
欠かせません</c.japanese>

654
00:51:42.933 --> 00:51:44.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>大丈夫</c.japanese>

655
00:51:44.726 --> 00:51:46.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>判断は間違ってない</c.japanese>

656
00:52:10.252 --> 00:52:11.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>やあ ライト</c.japanese>

657
00:52:13.213 --> 00:52:15.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>君は… Ｌだね</c.japanese>

658
00:52:16.299 --> 00:52:20.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>Ｌが本名ではないと
分かってますよね</c.japanese>

659
00:52:21.721 --> 00:52:23.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何しにここへ？</c.japanese>

660
00:52:23.849 --> 00:52:25.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜査です　君は？</c.japanese>

661
00:52:25.892 --> 00:52:28.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕は… 帰るところだ</c.japanese>

662
00:52:30.063 --> 00:52:32.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>困難な決断でしたか？</c.japanese>

663
00:52:32.858 --> 00:52:34.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何の決断？</c.japanese>

664
00:52:34.568 --> 00:52:36.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>父親を殺さないこと</c.japanese>

665
00:52:37.654 --> 00:52:38.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何の話？</c.japanese>

666
00:52:38.947 --> 00:52:42.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>不利になると分かっても
殺せなかった</c.japanese>

667
00:52:42.868 --> 00:52:46.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>君にその分別があって
よかった</c.japanese>

668
00:52:46.621 --> 00:52:51.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>おかげで君がキラだと
確信できましたから</c.japanese>

669
00:52:51.793 --> 00:52:53.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕がキラ？</c.japanese>

670
00:52:53.086 --> 00:52:53.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>明白です</c.japanese>

671
00:52:53.920 --> 00:52:56.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>だったら逮捕しろよ</c.japanese>

672
00:52:56.673 --> 00:53:01.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それは近いうちに
完全に追い詰めてからです</c.japanese>

673
00:53:01.887 --> 00:53:05.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そうか
好きなようにやればいいさ</c.japanese>

674
00:53:06.057 --> 00:53:07.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕はこれで…</c.japanese>

675
00:53:13.523 --> 00:53:14.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>教えてくれ</c.japanese>

676
00:53:18.236 --> 00:53:21.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラはどうやって殺してる？</c.japanese>

677
00:53:21.156 --> 00:53:23.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私が君に聞きたいですね</c.japanese>

678
00:53:23.950 --> 00:53:28.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私が思うに
君は離れた場所にいながら</c.japanese>

679
00:53:28.204 --> 00:53:31.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>超能力を使って
殺せるのでしょう</c.japanese>

680
00:53:31.875 --> 00:53:34.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>全く分からないんだろ？</c.japanese>

681
00:53:34.211 --> 00:53:36.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いずれ君自身が―</c.japanese>

682
00:53:36.963 --> 00:53:39.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私に教えてくれます</c.japanese>

683
00:53:39.507 --> 00:53:45.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>追い込まれたキラが 凶悪な
誰かに能力を渡していたら？</c.japanese>

684
00:53:45.555 --> 00:53:48.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>能力は渡せるんですね？</c.japanese>

685
00:53:48.391 --> 00:53:54.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラも君と同様 殺人を
終わらせたいのかもしれない</c.japanese>

686
00:53:54.940 --> 00:53:59.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラを追うより
助けたらどうなんだ？</c.japanese>

687
00:54:02.447 --> 00:54:03.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>助けろと</c.japanese>

688
00:54:07.994 --> 00:54:08.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いいですか？</c.japanese>

689
00:54:10.080 --> 00:54:14.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>取引を申し出るのは
優位に立っている側です</c.japanese>

690
00:54:15.126 --> 00:54:18.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>君は逮捕の時に
懇願でもすればいい</c.japanese>

691
00:54:19.089 --> 00:54:22.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何も分かってないくせに</c.japanese>

692
00:54:23.051 --> 00:54:25.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>こう考えたらどうでしょう</c.japanese>

693
00:54:26.012 --> 00:54:28.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>400人以上を
殺した犯人が―</c.japanese>

694
00:54:30.600 --> 00:54:33.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“仕方なかった”と
言い訳すれば</c.japanese>

695
00:54:34.020 --> 00:54:38.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラは犯人を許しますか？
それとも殺しますか？</c.japanese>

696
00:54:39.067 --> 00:54:41.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>キラを殺すつもりなんだな</c.japanese>

697
00:54:41.903 --> 00:54:45.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私は殺さない
銃を持つのもイヤだ</c.japanese>

698
00:54:45.865 --> 00:54:47.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>法に裁いてもらいます</c.japanese>

699
00:54:48.576 --> 00:54:52.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>どう裁かれるかは
犯した罪で決まる</c.japanese>

700
00:54:53.081 --> 00:54:57.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私は太陽へ飛ぶ君が
灰になるのを見届けます</c.japanese>

701
00:54:59.337 --> 00:55:00.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それでいいさ</c.japanese>

702
00:55:00.755 --> 00:55:04.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>このゲームに
引き分けはありません</c.japanese>

703
00:55:28.033 --> 00:55:29.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ごめんなさい</c.japanese>

704
00:55:29.284 --> 00:55:30.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>父さんだぞ</c.japanese>

705
00:55:30.285 --> 00:55:33.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私どうかしてた　怖かったの</c.japanese>

706
00:55:33.455 --> 00:55:35.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>僕は怖がってないと？</c.japanese>

707
00:55:36.791 --> 00:55:38.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>小さな存在の私に―</c.japanese>

708
00:55:39.210 --> 00:55:41.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなたは力をくれた</c.japanese>

709
00:55:42.464 --> 00:55:44.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あなたを失いたくなくて</c.japanese>

710
00:55:46.092 --> 00:55:47.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>あんなことを</c.japanese>

711
00:55:52.223 --> 00:55:53.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>愛してる</c.japanese>

712
00:56:01.691 --> 00:56:02.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>愛してるわ</c.japanese>

713
00:56:13.036 --> 00:56:14.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>Ｌの顔は見た</c.japanese>

714
00:56:14.954 --> 00:56:17.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>名前が分かれば止められる</c.japanese>

715
00:56:22.420 --> 00:56:23.171 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:71.69%,start 
<c.japanese>〝キラ捜査本部</c.japanese>
<c.japanese>記者会見〞</c.japanese>

716
00:56:23.171 --> 00:56:24.923 vertical:rl position:10.00%,start align:start size:80.00% line:71.69%,start 
<c.japanese>〝キラ捜査本部</c.japanese>
<c.japanese>記者会見〞</c.japanese>

717
00:56:23.171 --> 00:56:24.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>このワタリだけが
Ｌの本名を知っている</c.japanese>

718
00:56:24.923 --> 00:56:28.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>このワタリだけが
Ｌの本名を知っている</c.japanese>

719
00:56:33.807 --> 00:56:37.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ワタリはＬの本名を
明かさずにいられなくなる”</c.japanese>

720
00:56:38.645 --> 00:56:41.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“48時間 誰とも接触せず―”</c.japanese>

721
00:56:41.648 --> 00:56:44.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“情報を伝えるために―”</c.japanese>

722
00:56:44.484 --> 00:56:47.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“206-555-0166に電話する”</c.japanese>

723
00:56:47.362 --> 00:56:51.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“10月12日 午後７時に
彼は死ぬ”</c.japanese>

724
00:56:51.825 --> 00:56:53.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>死に方は？</c.japanese>

725
00:56:53.326 --> 00:56:54.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>運命に任せるさ</c.japanese>

726
00:56:54.786 --> 00:56:55.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>なに？</c.japanese>

727
00:56:55.620 --> 00:56:57.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>リュークに言った</c.japanese>

728
00:56:57.872 --> 00:56:59.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>名前のために殺す？</c.japanese>

729
00:56:59.624 --> 00:57:02.043 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いや　殺しはしない</c.japanese>

730
00:57:02.502 --> 00:57:07.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“ルール89　名前を書いた人が
そのページを破棄すれば”</c.japanese>

731
00:57:08.091 --> 00:57:09.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>“対象者は死なない”</c.japanese>

732
00:57:09.926 --> 00:57:14.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>10月12日 午後７時より前に
燃やせばいい</c.japanese>

733
00:57:14.639 --> 00:57:15.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>だろ？</c.japanese>

734
00:57:15.932 --> 00:57:18.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>できるのは１回きりだ</c.japanese>

735
00:57:19.519 --> 00:57:22.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>間違いを犯しても
２回目はない</c.japanese>

736
00:57:23.565 --> 00:57:25.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>１回で十分だ</c.japanese>

737
00:57:35.034 --> 00:57:36.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ワタリです</c.japanese>

738
00:57:36.453 --> 00:57:38.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>Ｌの本名は知りません</c.japanese>

739
00:57:38.955 --> 00:57:39.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何だって？</c.japanese>

740
00:57:40.039 --> 00:57:45.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>モントークの養護施設に
いた頃のことは分かりません</c.japanese>

741
00:57:45.378 --> 00:57:47.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ロチェスタープログラムです</c.japanese>

742
00:57:48.089 --> 00:57:50.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ロチェスタープログラム？</c.japanese>

743
00:57:50.258 --> 00:57:55.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>親を失った子を一流の探偵に
育てるプログラムです</c.japanese>

744
00:57:55.805 --> 00:57:56.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>まさか</c.japanese>

745
00:57:56.764 --> 00:57:57.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>本当です</c.japanese>

746
00:57:57.891 --> 00:58:01.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>厳しい条件の地下室で
７か月過ごし―</c.japanese>

747
00:58:02.395 --> 00:58:07.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>正気を保てた者だけが
プログラムに参加できます</c.japanese>

748
00:58:07.400 --> 00:58:11.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>Ｌは最年少の
６歳で入りました</c.japanese>

749
00:58:11.154 --> 00:58:14.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>それはいいから
Ｌの本名を教えろ</c.japanese>

750
00:58:14.908 --> 00:58:17.410 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>施設の個人ファイルに
あります</c.japanese>

751
00:58:17.577 --> 00:58:20.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>今すぐ施設に行ってくれ</c.japanese>

752
00:58:20.914 --> 00:58:22.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>でも休まないと</c.japanese>

753
00:58:22.707 --> 00:58:26.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>睡眠は良い推理に
欠かせません</c.japanese>

754
00:58:26.211 --> 00:58:29.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ダメだ
48時間以内に本名が要る</c.japanese>

755
00:58:29.714 --> 00:58:31.591 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>48時間後に何が？</c.japanese>

756
00:58:32.050 --> 00:58:33.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>すぐに行け</c.japanese>

757
00:58:33.426 --> 00:58:34.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>はい</c.japanese>

758
00:58:37.055 --> 00:58:38.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺した方がいい</c.japanese>

759
00:58:38.765 --> 00:58:39.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>心配するな</c.japanese>

760
00:58:41.392 --> 00:58:42.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>そんなのダメ</c.japanese>

761
00:58:43.770 --> 00:58:45.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>私も手伝うわ</c.japanese>

762
00:59:57.468 --> 00:59:59.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>シルクハットをかぶった</c.japanese>

763
00:59:59.762 --> 01:00:01.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>奥さんとダンスを？</c.japanese>

764
01:00:02.473 --> 01:00:06.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>いや　高校の頃は
振り向いてもらえなかった</c.japanese>

765
01:00:10.064 --> 01:00:12.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>どうも　席を外して</c.japanese>

766
01:00:12.650 --> 01:00:13.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何しに来た？</c.japanese>

767
01:00:14.110 --> 01:00:16.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>緊急の話し合いです</c.japanese>

768
01:00:17.530 --> 01:00:18.406 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>悪いな</c.japanese>

769
01:00:19.657 --> 01:00:21.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ライトは残ってください</c.japanese>

770
01:00:22.368 --> 01:00:24.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>君に関する話です</c.japanese>

771
01:00:24.329 --> 01:00:25.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>どんな話だ</c.japanese>

772
01:00:34.088 --> 01:00:35.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ワタリが消えました</c.japanese>

773
01:00:35.632 --> 01:00:41.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>彼が私に無断で
遠出することはあり得ません</c.japanese>

774
01:00:41.929 --> 01:00:42.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>電話しよう</c.japanese>

775
01:00:43.306 --> 01:00:44.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>目的は？</c.japanese>

776
01:00:44.140 --> 01:00:45.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何の話だか…</c.japanese>

777
01:00:45.642 --> 01:00:47.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>動揺してるんだな</c.japanese>

778
01:00:47.185 --> 01:00:48.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ライトがキラです</c.japanese>

779
01:00:50.563 --> 01:00:51.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>なに？</c.japanese>

780
01:00:51.230 --> 01:00:55.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>殺されないのはキラの
親だからだとも気付かない</c.japanese>

781
01:00:55.693 --> 01:00:58.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜査官ともあろう人が</c.japanese>

782
01:00:58.696 --> 01:00:59.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>帰ってくれ</c.japanese>

783
01:00:59.614 --> 01:01:00.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>断ります</c.japanese>

784
01:01:00.907 --> 01:01:01.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>何だと？</c.japanese>

785
01:01:01.532 --> 01:01:05.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>捜索令状がありますから
帰りません</c.japanese>

786
01:01:05.411 --> 01:01:07.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>今は君が優位です</c.japanese>

787
01:01:07.997 --> 01:01:13.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
<c.japanese>ワタリを無事返すなら
取引を受け入れてもいい</c.japanese>

788
01:01:13.753 --> 01:01:16.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:93.00%,end 
